   Category: Tax Credits and Deductions

   Part of being a good citizen, of course, is to pay your taxes. As a
   taxpayer and as a person with a disability, you should also know the
   credits and deductions to which you may be entitled. These sites also
   can provide you with the information you need to lessen your tax
   liability.

